## 6. Icon Components

**Figma Page:** `〰️ Icon` (`141:12807`)

The Design Kit ships two icon libraries:

### Lucide Icons
- **Figma path:** `Icon/Lucide/{icon-name}`
- **Usage in Nuxt UI:** `<UIcon name="i-lucide-{icon-name}" />`
- **Examples:** `i-lucide-arrow-right`, `i-lucide-check`, `i-lucide-x`, `i-lucide-chevron-down`, `i-lucide-search`, `i-lucide-user`, `i-lucide-settings`, `i-lucide-home`, `i-lucide-menu`, `i-lucide-bell`

### Simple Icons (Brand Icons)
- **Figma path:** `Icon/SimpleIcons/{icon-name}`
- **Usage in Nuxt UI:** `<UIcon name="i-simple-icons-{icon-name}" />`
- **Examples:** `i-simple-icons-github`, `i-simple-icons-twitter`, `i-simple-icons-nuxt`, `i-simple-icons-vue`, `i-simple-icons-typescript`

